   "pose_note": "Live grab is the current bind/animation pose only; GW skins in a vertex shader and GWCA exposes no skeleton. model_state/animation_id record the pose for provenance. Per-vertex bone indices+weights (chunk.weighted) are exported as OBJ #vbld lines when export_skin_weights is on -- that is the mesh->bone binding; the bone transforms are in the vertex-shader palette (enable probe_shader_constants to dump probe[]).",
